paragraphs.text:
%spark2.sql
SELECT parent_salary AS avg_parent_salary, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS college_goers, COUNT(*) AS total_population
FROM Studentview
GROUP BY parent_salary

%spark2.sql
SELECT parent_was_in_college, COUNT(*) AS total_population, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS future_college_goers
FROM Studentview
GROUP BY parent_was_in_college
ORDER BY parent_was_in_college

%spark2.sql
SELECT parent_age, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS college_goers, COUNT(*) AS total_population
FROM Studentview
GROUP BY parent_age order by parent_age

%spark2.sql
SELECT average_grades, COUNT(*) AS total_population, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS college_goers
FROM Studentview
GROUP BY average_grades
ORDER BY average_grades

%spark2.sql
SELECT type_school, COUNT(*) AS total_population, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS college_goers
FROM Sutdentview
GROUP BY type_school
ORDER BY type_school

%spark2.sql
SELECT school_accreditation, COUNT(*) AS total_population, SUM(will_go_to_college) AS college_goers
FROM Studentview
GROUP BY school_accreditation
ORDER BY school_accreditation
